            " 2, p.HasBias) +\n                                    BatchNormActivation(C + 1, " +
            "In(\"DC\", C + 1), p.Activation) +\n                                    strSE +\n   " +
            "                                 BatchNorm(C + 2, In(\"C\", C + 2)));\n\n           " +
